import * as React from "react"
import Svg, { G, Circle, Path, Defs } from "react-native-svg"

const SendSvg = (props) => (
  <Svg
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width={24}
    height={24}
    fill="none"
    {...props}
  >
    <G filter="url(#a)">
      <Circle cx={12} cy={11.25} r={11.25} fill="#fff" />
    </G>
    <Path
      stroke="#0076B9"
      strokeWidth={1.2}
      d="M19.5 11.25 9.75 4.5v7.5m9.75 0L9.75 19.5V11.25m9.75 0H9.75"
    />
    <Path
      stroke="#000"
      strokeOpacity={0.2}
      strokeWidth={1.2}
      d="M19.5 11.25 9.75 4.5v7.5m9.75 0L9.75 19.5V11.25m9.75 0H9.75"
    />
    <Defs></Defs>
  </Svg>
)

export default SendSvg
